list_for_each_entry_rcu has built-in RCU and lock checking. Make use of
it in driver core.

Acked-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>
Signed-off-by: Joel Fernandes (Google) <joel@joelfernandes.org>
